==Organizations==
National organizations
* BirdLife Australia (previously known as Birds Australia) is the leading Australian NGO for birds, birding, ornithology and conservation, formed by a merger of the Royal Australasian Ornithologists Union and Bird Observation &amp; Conservation Australia
* Australian Bird Study Association, for banders and other field ornithologists
* Birding-Aus - an Internet mailing list about Australian birds

Australian regional and state organisations
* Australian Capital Territory
